directions: Blend zucchini, lemon juice, tahini, garlic, and salt in a blender until creamy. Stream olive oil into the hummus while blending until completely incorporated. Continue blending until smooth, 1 to 2 minutes. Transfer to a serving bowl; sprinkle cumin and paprika over the hummus.
ingredients: 2 small zucchini, peeled and cut into chunks
title: Creamy Zucchini Hummus
